data.description: Turn-key classic brick home in popular Raintree Estates!   Are you looking for a mother-in-law suite or a double primary suite home? This gem of a home  is for you! Lots  of space, excellent location, and the perks of a a fenced back yard with a private pool and lanai! Four large bedrooms, including two oversized master suites, a den/office, formal dining, family room, bonus room, spacious kitchen (granite counters, tile backsplash and stainless appliances added in 2021) with bar and cozy breakfast nook. Everything you want for elegant indoor and outdoor living: Your spacious great room with with fireplace and soaring ceilings opens via your sliding glass door directly onto the  screened-in lanai which overlooks your sparkling pool. The shady generous backyard is fully fenced. This one-story home on .28 acres with sprinkler system has been meticulously maintained. Raintree Estates also boasts a special gem; a community beach/park on the bay with an outdoor fire-pit, picnic tables, pavilion and more! Come make your move today.
